    <rigor-reason>Production playbook canvas data model change; consumed by `DeliverOutput` node executor (NFR-08-protected â€” executor itself unmodified); gates 4 downstream data migrations + CapabilityRouter dedup.</rigor-reason>
    <parallel-group>B-G1</parallel-group>
