    <constraint source="project">Backward compatibility â€” nodes WITHOUT `destination` MUST default to `chat` (current behavior). Migration of existing playbook node JSON to add explicit defaults is OPTIONAL; existing nodes work unchanged.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">`widgetType` is conditionally required: required when `destination = workspace`; ignored otherwise. Document this rule in the schema contract.</constraint>
  </constraints>

